  <title>Change the default password keyring</title>

  <p>When you
  <link xref="passwords-stored-new-create">create a new stored password</link>,
  it is stored in the <gui>Login</gui> keyring by default unless you choose
  another keyring. You can make any other keyring the default choice in
  <app>Passwords and Keys</app>.</p>

  <steps>
    <title>To change the default keyring:</title>
      <item>
	<p>Select <guiseq><gui style="menu">View</gui>
	<gui style="menuitem">By keyring</gui></guiseq>.</p>
      </item>
      <item>
	<p>From the left, select the keyring of your choice from the list.</p>
      </item>
      <item>
	<p>Right click on the selected keyring and select
	<gui>Set as default</gui>.</p>
      </item>
  </steps>

